261
0:12:48,14 --> 0:12:50,8
confronted their illusions.


262
0:12:50,8 --> 0:12:52,39
Other times, the blackmail's reactive.


263
0:12:52,39 --> 0:12:55,87
The blackmailer tries to stifle any further
challenge with the same manipulative


264
0:12:55,87 --> 0:12:56,92
methods --


265
0:12:56,92 --> 0:13:0,4
