269
0:13:9,8 --> 0:13:14,15
the poorly constructed illusion can only survive by blocking


270
0:13:14,15 --> 0:13:14,96
them out.


271
0:13:14,96 --> 0:13:19,42
Having reflected on this death denial
over several years, it was intriguing to


272
0:13:19,42 --> 0:13:23,79
come across experimental support last
