273
0:13:23,79 --> 0:13:26,98
the work of Sheldon Solomon, Tom Pyszczynski


274
0:13:26,98 --> 0:13:28,7
and Jeff Greenberg --


275
0:13:28,7 --> 0:13:36,39
the proponents of 'terror management
theory'.


276
0:13:36,39 --> 0:13:38,199
Sheldon Solomon explains:


277
0:13:38,199 --> 0:13:41,12
'If culture serves a death-denying function


278
0:13:41,12 --> 0:13:43,32
then if you remind people that they're going to die,


