0:13:43,32 --> 0:13:46,86
that should momentarily .... increase the
need for the death-denying aspects of


280
0:13:46,86 --> 0:13:48,91
their particular beliefs about reality --


281
0:13:48,91 --> 0:13:52,47
and that should be reflected by their
reactions to other individuals, who


282
0:13:52,47 --> 0:13:54,86
either bolster or support those beliefs,


283
0:13:54,86 --> 0:13:58,79
or who undermine those beliefs by either
being hostile to them,


284
0:13:58,79 --> 0:14:0,37
or merely different from them.


285
0:14:0,37 --> 0:14:3,25
The terror management team have
