292
0:14:20,98 --> 0:14:24,9
Both groups were then asked for their
impressions of two fictitious students


293
0:14:24,9 --> 0:14:27,1
who shared personality traits.


294
0:14:27,1 --> 0:14:28,589
One student was a christian.


295
0:14:28,589 --> 0:14:30,3
The other was jewish.


296
0:14:30,3 --> 0:14:33,51
Subjects who'd been reminded of their own
death gave an especially positive


297
0:14:33,51 --> 0:14:37,51
